---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="LDR Visa — U.S. Visa Guides for International Couples"
  description="Plain-English guides for K-1 fiancé visas, CR-1 spousal visas, affidavit of support, bona fide marriage evidence, and adjustment of status — updated for 2026."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-badge">Updated for 2026 · K-1 &amp; CR-1</div>
      <h1>The U.S. Visa Guide for<br/><span>Long-Distance Couples</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Understand processing times, income requirements, interview prep, and every form — without the legalese.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/k1-vs-cr1" class="btn-primary">Which visa do I need? →</a>
        <a href="/k1-visa" class="btn-secondary">K-1 Fiancé Visa Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">12–18 mo</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Avg. K-1 total timeline</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">$25,550</div>
        <div class="stat-label">2026 income floor (family of 2)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">90 days</div>
        <div class="stat-label">To marry after K-1 entry</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">5 stages</div>
        <div class="stat-label">From petition to green card</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Decision: K-1 vs CR-1 -->
  <section class="decision">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Start Here</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Which visa path is right for you?</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">The answer depends on whether you're engaged or already married. Both paths lead to a green card — the route is different.</p>
      <div class="decision-grid">

        <div class="decision-card featured">
          <span class="card-tag">Not married yet</span>
          <h3>K-1 Fiancé Visa</h3>
          <p>Your U.S. citizen partner files a petition so you can enter the U.S., get married within 90 days, then apply for a green card.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Petition → NVC → Embassy interview</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Avg. 12–18 months total</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Must marry within 90 days of entry</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> File I-129F to start</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/k1-visa" class="card-link">Full K-1 guide →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="decision-card">
          <span class="card-tag">Already married</span>
          <h3>CR-1 / IR-1 Spousal Visa</h3>
          <p>Your U.S. citizen or LPR spouse sponsors you for an immigrant visa. You arrive in the U.S. as a permanent resident.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Petition → NVC → Consular processing</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Avg. 14–24 months total</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Arrive with green card (IR-1) or conditional (CR-1)</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> File I-130 to start</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/cr1-visa" class="card-link">Full CR-1 guide →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="decision-card">
          <span class="card-tag">Compare both</span>
          <h3>K-1 vs CR-1: Side by Side</h3>
          <p>Cost, timeline, pros and cons — every difference explained so you can make the right call for your situation.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Full cost breakdown</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Processing time comparison</div>
            <div class="card-meta-item"><span class="dot"></span> Which is faster in 2026?</div>
          </div>
          <a href="/k1-vs-cr1" class="card-link">See comparison →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Timeline -->
  <section class="timeline-strip">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">K-1 Process Overview</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">How the K-1 visa works, step by step</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Five stages from filing to green card. Each has its own forms, fees, and wait times.</p>
      <div class="timeline-steps">
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-title">File I-129F</div>
          <div class="step-time">~7–12 months</div>
          <div class="step-desc">U.S. citizen files petition at USCIS</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-title">NVC Transfer</div>
          <div class="step-time">~3–6 weeks</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Case moves to National Visa Center</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-title">Embassy Interview</div>
          <div class="step-time">~1–3 months</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Interview at U.S. consulate abroad</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <div class="step-title">Entry + Marriage</div>
          <div class="step-time">Within 90 days</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Enter U.S. and get married</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step">
          <div class="step-num">5</div>
          <div class="step-title">Adjust Status</div>
          <div class="step-time">~12–24 months</div>
          <div class="step-desc">File for green card (Form I-485)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Topics Grid -->
  <section class="topics">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">All Topics</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to know</h2>
      <div class="topics-grid">

        <a href="/k1-visa-processing-time" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">⏱</div>
          <h3>K-1 Processing Time 2026</h3>
          <p>Current USCIS and NVC wait times, by country.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/affidavit-of-support" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Affidavit of Support (I-864)</h3>
          <p>Income requirements, poverty guidelines, and common mistakes.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/bona-fide-marriage" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">💑</div>
          <h3>Bona Fide Marriage Evidence</h3>
          <p>The 4 pillars, photo tips, letter templates, and real examples.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/k1-visa-interview" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">🎤</div>
          <h3>K-1 Interview Prep</h3>
          <p>70+ questions, best answers, and what to bring.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/adjustment-of-status" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">🟢</div>
          <h3>Adjustment of Status</h3>
          <p>When to file, processing times, fees, and the 90-day rule.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/i-129f" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">📋</div>
          <h3>Form I-129F</h3>
          <p>Instructions, checklist, evidence examples, and sample answers.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/cr1-visa-processing-time" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">📅</div>
          <h3>CR-1 Processing Time 2026</h3>
          <p>Current wait times for spousal visa processing.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/k1-visa-denial-reasons" class="topic-card">
          <div class="topic-icon">⚠️</div>
          <h3>K-1 Denial Reasons</h3>
          <p>The most common reasons for rejection and how to avoid them.</p>
          <span class="topic-arrow">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Popular guides list -->
  <section class="guides">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Popular Guides</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Most-read articles</h2>
      <div class="guides-list">

        <a href="/k1-visa-processing-time" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">K-1 Visa</span>
            <span class="guide-title">K-1 Visa Processing Time 2026: USCIS + NVC + Embassy Breakdown</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/affidavit-of-support-income-requirements" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">I-864</span>
            <span class="guide-title">2026 Affidavit of Support Income Requirements (Poverty Guidelines)</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/4-pillars-of-evidence-partner-visa" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">Evidence</span>
            <span class="guide-title">The 4 Pillars of Evidence for a Partner Visa — What USCIS Wants to See</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/k1-visa-interview-questions" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">Interview</span>
            <span class="guide-title">70 K-1 Visa Interview Questions (With the Best Answers)</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/adjustment-of-status-after-marriage" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">AOS</span>
            <span class="guide-title">Adjustment of Status After Marriage: Timeline, Fees &amp; New Rules 2026</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/k1-vs-cr1" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">Compare</span>
            <span class="guide-title">K-1 vs CR-1 Visa: Cost, Timeline &amp; Which is Faster in 2026?</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/i-129f-checklist" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">I-129F</span>
            <span class="guide-title">Form I-129F Complete Checklist: Documents, Evidence &amp; Sample Answers</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/bona-fide-marriage-letter" class="guide-item">
          <div class="guide-info">
            <span class="guide-cat">Evidence</span>
            <span class="guide-title">Bona Fide Marriage Letter Template from Friends and Family (Free Download)</span>
          </div>
          <span class="guide-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
